OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItaly waters down windfall 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftax on banks               
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy has watered down plans to hit its
OL,6, banks with a windfall tax, leading to a
OL,7, rebound in the share prices of the     
OL,8, country's lenders.                     
OL,10,FOn Monday night, the government passed 
OL,11,Fa one-off 40% tax on the profits banks 
OL,12,Fearn from higher interest rates, in a  
OL,13,Fshock move that saw shares plummet.    
OL,15,FIt said proceeds would be used to help 
OL,16,Fmortgage holders and to cut taxes.     
OL,18,FBut late on Tuesday evening, the       
OL,19,Ffinance ministry said the tax would be 
OL,20,Fcapped at 0.1% of assets.              
